Perfect! Here's a comprehensive summary of all the components with their interfaces and props:

---

## 1. BasicScreen (Template)

**Location:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/src/atomic/templates/BasicScreen/`

### Interface: `BasicScreenProps`
```typescript
interface BasicScreenProps {
  children: ReactNode;
  title: string;
  titleColor?: string;
  leftIcon?: PropsIcon['name'];
  hasLeftIcon?: boolean;
  leftIconOnPress?: () => void;
  leftIconColor?: string;
  rightIcon?: PropsIcon['name'];
  rightIconColor?: string;
  hasRightIcon?: boolean;
  rightIconOnPress?: () => void;
  bgColor?: ColorToken;
  statusBarBg?: ColorToken;
  statusBarProps?: PropsStatusBar;
  hasScroll?: boolean;
  scrollViewProps?: ScrollViewProps;
  hasNativeGoBack?: boolean;
  nativeGoBackFn?: () => void;
  hasHeader?: boolean;
  headerTitle?: string;
  isLoading?: boolean;
  testID?: string;
  throttle?: number;
  showValue?: boolean;
  setShowValue?: (e: boolean) => void;
  rightSecondaryIcon?: PropsIcon['name'];
  rightSecondaryIconNot?: PropsIcon['name'];
  rightSecondaryIconOnPress?: () => void;
  errorButtonOnPress: () => void;
  hasError?: boolean;
  handleGoToHome?: () => void;
  currentRouteName?: string;
  handleClose?: () => void;
  scrollViewRef?: RefObject<ScrollView>;
}
```

### Key Features:
- Wraps content with a keyboard-avoiding container
- Renders StatusBar + optional Header with navigation icons
- Optional HeaderTitle section (alternative to standard header)
- Loading modal overlay ("Aguarde...")
- Error modal overlay with retry and home navigation buttons
- Optional ScrollView wrapper
- Right secondary icon toggle support
- Used by hook pattern: index.tsx (logic) + view.tsx (render)

---

## 2. ApiError (Organism)

**Location:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/src/atomic/organisms/ApiError/`

### Interface: `ApiErrorProps`
```typescript
interface ApiErrorProps {
  title?: string;
  subTitle?: string;
  onPress: () => void;
  hasBackToHome?: boolean;
  isLoading?: boolean;
  testID?: string;
  targetScreen?: keyof PropsRootStack;
}

interface ApiErrorViewProps extends ApiErrorProps {
  handleNavigateToHome: () => void;
}
```

### Default Values:
- `title = 'Ocorreu um erro inesperado'`
- `subTitle = 'Por favor, espere alguns minutos ou tente novamente.'`
- `hasBackToHome = true`
- `isLoading = false`
- `testID = 'ApiErrorView'`
- `targetScreen = 'Home'`

### What It Renders:
- Centered error layout with either:
  - Error image (188x188) when `hasBackToHome = true`
  - Red alert icon box when `hasBackToHome = false`
- Large title text (subtitleXXXXL)
- Optional subtitle text (paragraphXXL)
- "Tentar novamente" button (primary, with loading state)
- "Voltar para a home" button (ghost, only if `hasBackToHome = true`)

---

## 3. PointsInfoBottomSheet (Organism)

**Location:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/src/atomic/organisms/PointsInfoBottomSheet/`

### Interface: `PointsInfoBottomSheetProps`
```typescript
interface PointsInfoBottomSheetProps {
  modalizeRef: React.RefObject<PropsModalizeRef>;
}
```

### What It Renders:
- BackDropBottom sheet (30% of window height)
- Informational text: "Os seus pontos ganhos ficam disponíveis no saldo sempre que você pagar sua próxima fatura."
- "Entendi" button that closes the modal
- Uses design-system components: BackDropBottom, Button, Text

---

## 4. LearnMorePointsSection (Organism)

**Location:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/dev/rnm-app-fintech-rewardprogram/src/atomic/organisms/LearnMorePointsSection/`

### Interface: `LearnMorePointsSectionViewProps`
```typescript
interface LearnMorePointsSectionViewProps {
  data?: ParameterPointsProgramResponse[];
  isLoading: boolean;
  isError: boolean;
  onPress: (question: string) => void;
  width: number;
}
```

### Data Type: `ParameterPointsProgramResponse`
- `category: string` (used as title)
- `value: ParameterPointsProgramValue` (contains icon)

### What It Renders:
- **Title:** "Saiba mais" (paragraphXXXL)
- **Loading State:** Renders 4 skeleton loaders (each 72px height)
- **Error State:** Returns null (no rendering)
- **Data State:** FlatList of CardActivity components
  - Each card shows category name
  - Icon from data.value
  - Right arrow icon ("icon-next")
  - OnPress triggers navigation to 'LearnMoreRewardProgram' with analytics

### Hook Logic (index.tsx):
- Reads from Zustand store: `parameterPointsProgram` (data + status)
- Handles category selection and analytics
- Passes down view props: data, isLoading, isError, onPress, width

---

## Summary for Storybook Usage

**Required Imports:**
```typescript
import BasicScreen from 'src/atomic/templates/BasicScreen';
import ApiError from 'src/atomic/organisms/ApiError';
import PointsInfoBottomSheet from 'src/atomic/organisms/PointsInfoBottomSheet';
import LearnMorePointsSection from 'src/atomic/organisms/LearnMorePointsSection';
```

